## ❌ Known Failed Approaches

### Modal Issues

| Problem | DON'T Do | DO Instead |
|---------|----------|------------|
| System slow | "Upgrade Modal plan" | Add keep-warm function |
| Multiple apps | "They can coexist" | Consolidate to ONE app |
| Function timeout | "Optimize code first" | Increase timeout parameter |

### Database Issues

| Problem | DON'T Do | DO Instead |
|---------|----------|------------|
| Low outreach (5/192) | "Rate limiting working" | Check for ID filters |
| Empty tables | "Must be working somewhere" | Find missing .insert() |
| Slow queries | "Switch databases" | Add indexes |

